2011年4月，德國外長[[韋斯特韋勒|韋斯特韋勒]]、英國外交大臣[[威廉·黑格|威廉·黑格]]、[[法國外交部|法國外交部]]、[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]先后通过外交渠道要求立即釋放艾未未<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/apr/04/ai-weiwei-germany-france-call-for-release |title=Ai Weiwei: France and Germany lead calls for Chinese artist's release| date =2011-04-04| language= |publisher=guardian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fco.gov.uk/en/news/latest-news/?view=News&id=579056182 |title=Foreign Secretary statement on the detention of Ai Weiwei in China| date =2011-04-04| language= |publisher=British Foreign & Commonwealth Office}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/chinaartpoliticsrightsus |title=US urges China to release dissident Ai Weiwei| date =2011-04-04| language=|publisher=AFP}}</ref>；4月21日，駐華大使[[洪博培|洪博培]]在[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]][[時代百大人物|時代百大人物]]評選中為艾未未撰文<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2066367_2066369_2066464,00.html |title=Ai Weiwei | date =2011-04-21 | accessdate =2011-04-21 |language= |publisher=TIME}}</ref>。6月4日，[[中華民國總統|中華民國總統]][[馬英九|馬英九]]發表[[六四事件|六四事件]]紀念專文，並提到希望大陸當局早日釋放劉曉波、艾未未<ref>{{cite news | language = | url =http://www.president.gov.tw/Default.aspx?tabid=131&itemid=24521&rmid=514 | title=總統發表「六四」感言| publisher = [[中華民國總統府|中華民國總統府]]| date =2011-06-04| accessdate =2011-06-05}}</ref>等等；4月4日，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指​​艾未未遭到拘捕沒有任何理由<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/news-and-updates/china-detains-ai-weiwei-warning-against-dissent-2011-04-04 |title=CHINA DETAINS AI WEIWEI AS WARNING AGAINST DISSENT| date =2011-04-04| language= |publisher=Amnesty International}}</ref>；4月6日，[[人权观察组织|人权观察组织]]要求中国政府立即释放艾未未<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hrw.org/ja/news/2011/04/06-3 |title=中国：立即释放艺术家、批评家艾未未 |accessdate=2011-04-06 |publisher=Human Rights Watch |language= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110416003823/http://www.hrw.org/ja/news/2011/04/06-3 |archivedate=2011-04-16 }}</ref>。6月9日，艾未未部分专访在[[日内瓦|日内瓦]]召开的[[联合国人权理事会|联合国人权理事会]]会议上首次公开<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/Ai-Weiwei-interview-screened-apf-3171260438.html |title=Ai Weiwei interview screened publicly for 1st time |accessdate=2011-06-10|publisher=Associated Press |language= }}</ref>；6月22日，國際特赦組織亞太地區呼吁释放文涛、胡明芬、刘正刚和张劲松等其他4名被非法羁押的人员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/news-and-updates/chinese-government-attempts-deflect-criticism-ai-weiwei-release-2011-06-22 |title=CHINESE GOVERNMENT ATTEMPTS TO DEFLECT CRITICISM WITH AI WEIWEI RELEASE| date =2011-06-22| language= |publisher=Amnesty International}}</ref>。

